  <brief_title>Parental Coping With Challenging Behavior in Mucopolysaccharidosis Type I-III</brief_title>
  <official_title>Behavioral Challenges in Children With Mucopolysaccharidosis Type I-III and Parental Coping Strategies</official_title>
